{"tid":1631912,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陶傑有說話 - 下一個戰場，是區議會選舉，不是街頭某些商店櫥窗和銀行鐵閘","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T08:27:47.000Z","uid":70194,"like":98,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"a009c44f5b766c7c4ffdf77beefed5d18a65c58a","tid":1631912,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"午夜旺角，雨中街頭。有如雨果小說和音樂劇「悲慘世界」的街頭抗爭場面。<br />\n形勢混亂，顯然有林鄭及其幕後勢力的臥底，混入抗爭對伍中，令暴力不斷升級。<br />\n請年輕人現在跟保持冷靜。記着：下一個戰場，是區議會選舉，不是街頭某些商店櫥窗和銀行鐵閘。Be Water，應該柔軟的時候，要柔軟，不必，也不可，時時都維持剛烈。Be courageous, but also be smart !<br />\n願大家平安。<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.533448593394335/3054742417931594/?type=3&amp;permPage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftokit.channel%2Fphotos%2Fa.533448593394335%2F3054742417931594%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26permPage%3D1&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsLwx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=37d60285\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.533448593394335/3054742417931594/?type=3&amp;permPage=1</a>"},{"pid":"bd1715fe6da8145bd872d53ccfe45c1f15e983e6","tid":1631912,"uid":70194,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:14.000Z","msg":"下一個戰場，是區議會選舉，不是街頭某些商店櫥窗和銀行鐵閘。Be Water，應該柔軟的時候，要柔軟，不必，也不可，時時都維持剛烈。"},{"pid":"e12c370473f3bb8f490bb98bd02a94dba2976951","tid":1631912,"uid":127379,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TQCvuAu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTQCvuAu.jpg&h=d3562576&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2b14d88c76a0dc10515aa1d9c793285d67aae4d","tid":1631912,"uid":15259,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"a78410da4bcba6160433a8945193bc690aaceedc","tid":1631912,"uid":253016,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"仲有得選先講野啦<br />\n連個選舉都DQ埋你呀"},{"pid":"1e0180a86f266f82510960e938d900268d73bd57","tid":1631912,"uid":1102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9df8fc7b7361ae2ed228b5e46be58c37353c727","tid":1631912,"uid":36775,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:15.000Z","msg":"區議會就廢<br />\n不過忍下手唔好亂私了同埋爆鋪"},{"pid":"d6931bebb04fedd7b2bdd89416a62284ef062f21","tid":1631912,"uid":28435,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"食義士人血饅頭"},{"pid":"48b1e0bc025196d28d078b676da358437fd3e969","tid":1631912,"uid":70194,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"唔係話割, 亦都唔係要屌邊個. 我地必須要小心令暴力不斷升級係咪對整場運動最有幫助. 18區多點開花, 但需要前線更有智慧的去在開花上讓運動繼續下去!"},{"pid":"026eed5d8ca961d1df7998b7476e601aa7f6c217","tid":1631912,"uid":320881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:09.000Z","msg":"P牌求幫推<br />\n<br />\n[正視聽] 每個動作嘅&quot;用途&quot;及&quot;代價&quot;<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631863</a>"},{"pid":"63bf94418fc54882d131efb0b7db4a882bb63f4e","tid":1631912,"uid":263625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2b14d88c76a0dc10515aa1d9c793285d67aae4d","tid":1631912,"uid":15259,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知