quo;s increasingly violent pro-democracy protests<br />\n<br />\n再係咁落去，美國人權及民主法案好可能被否決。"},{"pid":"d1bdc0d0066811ed501d233db5b4ee1e766b4ecc","tid":1631912,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2490e1565e2abd710bc23f46e83155cb855cc79","tid":1631912,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f3cdf354b30cdccd79c3d4364dba916a71a5a95","tid":1631912,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"同建制妥協係多鳩餘 曬鳩氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:14.000Z","msg":"而家係要打建制. 將建制既其中一個資金來源切斷. 同佢爭地區餅仔食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"議會就係建制一部份"},{"pid":"ccef0976e3bdbfa5dd6dca896c6b3b00b795279c","tid":1631912,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d97582c7296dc7bb6ea30d65bcba7bd2a78e4ed","tid":1631912,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9df8fc7b7361ae2ed228b5e46be58c37353c727","tid":1631912,"uid":36775,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:15.000Z","msg":"區議會就廢<br />\n不過忍下手唔好亂私了同埋爆鋪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:51.000Z","msg":"調整裝修同私了可以<br />\n但都唔係為區議會咁搞笑嘛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:05:34.000Z","msg":"當然係為人權法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bde947b0a7ed225535e56a26873af771410c13","tid":1631912,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9436a7f50ac5556c33eb7714ef7b7f4d0537e2cc","tid":1631912,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"268491435840a2e616f1e56ba9527d596ddda134","tid":1631912,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"最後直路， 我建議係智取"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20