time&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsLwx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=a79480b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3027838/violence-blew-lid-hong-kongs-simmering-discontent-its-about-time</a><br />\n連一個咁嘅人都讚嘅時候其他人仲會轉風向？<br />\n聯合國係人都知廢嘅幾多貪污唔再話下<br />\n一個冇牙力嘅人講乜都晒氣<br />\n眾議員議長都未出聲<br />\n當日左膠上身組人鏈嘅gohone都冇出聲<br />\n大左膠楊俊賢冇割席<br />\n大大個P牌講咩轉風向<br />\n擺明就係共媒01網軍<br />\n01吹咩風你班P牌就全部帶咩風<br />\n唔使唔認啦你<br />\n【偵探、長文】操縱連登風向既黑手　好可能係香港01<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632038\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632038</a>"},{"pid":"ef2f0dbe00c95bb5ce53d48273424468d685dab0","tid":1631912,"uid":277540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:45:38.000Z","msg":"借位POST <br />\n<br />\n劉師齊師傅係 2/9 幫手足卜左支卦 佢都好得架 大家聽下支卦講咩野啦  要守紀律呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L0QGpXyECro&amp;t=1502s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL0QGpXyECro%26t%3D1502s&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsLwx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=932de569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L0QGpXyECro&amp;t=1502s</a>"},{"pid":"56fd66a46a5b602260dfe26013add33bf0080a74","tid":1631912,"uid":45305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:16:54.000Z","msg":"我愛19"},{"pid":"31b8550b44f362d1a8fe1153b2cbf450fbe6a8fb","tid":1631912,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:54:52.000Z","msg":"係持久戰，今日我哋嚟做好文宣先"},{"pid":"d873dac8e4e38d8b2e67559dbf8a40b8f758e6b9","tid":1631912,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"[重要] 林奠同POPO想重演721，屈手足兄弟，唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633895\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633895</a>"},{"pid":"8e22b67aa91915c5a78141b572d7d96db06f5fd6","tid":1631912,"uid":295865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:10:48.000Z","msg":"講真每種方法都要試，區議會投票係立法會既基礎，建制想押後好明顯係真係驚，敵人驚既我地越要做"},{"pid":"f30e5a9a74e2945ce8022c3ec